{"tid":970514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"排隊起爭執　撳機男捱拳傷頭","createTime":"2019-01-06T01:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T02:19:33.000Z","uid":122,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"78b487e21b4b1c81309ca1cff5ce3a9fc23e3e1b","tid":970514,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:25:41.000Z","msg":"今日(6日)凌晨接近3時，一名姓陳(39歲)男子在旺角彌敦道618號好望角大廈一間銀行櫃員機提款，期間疑他良久「未搞掂」，惹來跟隨其後另一男子不滿，雙方頓起衝突，一輪互罵後，陳遭對方揮拳襲擊，頭部受傷流血，涉案男子逃去。警員接報抵達現場調查，並於西洋菜南街尋獲遇襲事主，惟經兜截無發現，遂將傷者送院治理。 <br />\n<br />\n警員調查後將案件列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，並通緝在逃男子，他年約30歲，身高約1.6米、中等身材，案發時身穿黑色上衣及黑色長褲。"},{"pid":"0ae56090ec103a40d0c25716e5eb8bf00bf2a05c","tid":970514,"uid":223256,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"幻想對白:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喂前面你禁完機未架? 成三個字啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關你撚事咩? 屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母x n<br />\n跟住打"},{"pid":"dd21ddb7c95a57d9de3f8cfb00d204f70158e760","tid":970514,"uid":35014,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:29:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da7e0b1c53e11303c3b5ee4e6d0e5988925e4cdb","tid":970514,"uid":223256,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"並通緝在逃男子，他年約30歲，身高約1.6米<br />\n<br />\n曾牠首<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32cc041e8407730591df8ec20574e0781c933cdd","tid":970514,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:44:36.000Z","msg":"比個矮仔打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n柒"},{"pid":"de3a2d5563c8319098aa972e6b5fbd960848a68f","tid":970514,"uid":37458,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦 阻撚住曬"},{"pid":"252b2ef151bd2bbf751a62167859